ReleaseMB Btn1

LocatePointer ChildWidgetSelectionDialog RSelectionListItem 13
ClickMB Btn1
LocatePointer ChildWidgetSelectionDialog ROkButton
ClickMB Btn1


CompareVisual Notebook

